patch.description:
Bulk update multiple folders at once.
Only analysts, validation leads, and maintainers can update folders.

Example request body:
{
    "updates": [
        {
            "id": "f-1",
            "name": "Updated Folder Name",
            "parentId": "f-2"
        }
    ]
}

Bulk update multiple tests at once.
Only analysts, validation leads, and maintainers can update tests.

Example request body:
{
    "updates": [
        {
            "id": "t-1",
            "name": "Updated Test Name",
            "status": "ACTIVE",
            "priority": "P1"
        }
    ]
}

Bulk update multiple cycle items at once.
Only analysts, validation leads, and maintainers can update cycle items.

Example request body:
{
    "updates": [
        {
            "id": "ci-1",
            "assigneeId": "u-4",
            "result": "PASSED",
            "map": "Detroit",
            "configurations": ["Vanilla"]
        }
    ]
}

Bulk update, create, and delete maps.
Only analysts, validation leads, and maintainers can manage maps.

Example request body:
{
    "updates": [
        {"old_name": "Detroit", "new_name": "Detroit Updated"}
    ],
    "creates": [
        {"name": "New Map"}
    ],
    "deletes": ["Old Map"]
}
